"body": "**Must know**\n- $U=\\dfrac{1}{2}CV^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}QV=\\dfrac{Q^2}{2C}$.\n- The energy is stored in the field, with energy density $u=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\varepsilon_0 E^2$.\n**Exam traps**\n- Choose the right form: $U=\\dfrac{Q^2}{2C}$ at constant charge, $U=\\dfrac{1}{2}CV^2$ at constant voltage.",
